episodes.title: IRONY WARNING: Former Cult Leader Reveals How He Escaped Needy Followers
episodes.description:
When Glensard Handswith first founded The Precious Order, it was bliss. But it soon turned into a nightmare. Hear how the man once known as Pandit Shiromani was able to break free and escape his followers, who were becoming super clingy.
